				<h1>Obtaining a Mortgage</h1>
				<p>A Step-by-Step Guide to Understanding the Mortgage Process<br /></p>
			</div>
	<img src="../images/Bolt/Checklist.gif" onMouseover="this.style.display='none'" alt="Bolt" style="float:left;padding:10px 10px 0 0;">
	<p>Although each mortgage is unique, they all
	follow the same steps. The chart below shows what YOU'RE doing and what
	WE'RE doing, during the 
	processing period before loan funding.</p>

	 <p>Many homeowners like you wonder where the mortgage loan
	 process begins and where it ends. Depending on the efficiency of the
	 outside vendors and suppliers we use in your community for the legal &amp; title
	 work, and the real estate appraisals generally three to four weeks, start-to-finish is
	 common.</p>
	<div class="Lcolumn">
<div style='margin:0;width:330px;'>
<b class="top"><b class="b1"></b><b class="b2"></b><b class="b3"></b><b class="b4"></b></b>
<h2 style='width:328px;'>You Do This</h2>
<b class="bottom"><b class="b4"></b><b class="b3"></b><b class="b2"></b><b class="b1"></b></b></div></div>

	<div class="Rcolumn">
<div style='margin:0;width:330px;'>
<b class="top"><b class="b1"></b><b class="b2"></b><b class="b3"></b><b class="b4"></b></b>
<h2 style='width:328px;'>This Happens</h2>
<b class="bottom"><b class="b4"></b><b class="b3"></b><b class="b2"></b><b class="b1"></b></b></div></div>

	<ul style="margin:0 1em;">
	<div class="Lcolumn" style="height:8em;">
		<li><p>You send us a loan application from this web site
		(<a href="../MortgageApplication/LoanAppShort.htm">Apply Now</a>) 24 hours
		a day, 7 days a week.</p></li></div>
	<div class="Rcolumn" style="height:150px;">
		<li><p>Our Loan Underwriting Department receives the
		application. Our Credit Analyst reviews the application and pre-qualifies
		your loan requestbased on the preliminary information you have provided to us. We do not pull credit 
		unless we are confident we can close the loan and we phone or email you that day with the Good News!</p></li></div>
	<div class="Lcolumn" style="height:5.5em;">
		<li><p>You collect the necessary paperwork from your records (Click on
		<a href="Documentation.php">Documentation</a> to create a personal list) and
		fax it (866-822-8500) to our office.</p></li></div>
	<div class="Rcolumn" style="height:5.5em;">
		<li><p>Our Loan Processing Department quality controls the paperwork, orders
		the appraisal, the legal &amp; title work, gets final approval, etc.</p></li></div>
	<div class="Lcolumn" style="height:5em;">
		<li><p>You meet the home appraiser at your home for the on-site inspection.
		See	<a href="Appraisals.htm">The Art Of Appraisals</a> to learn about this
		necessary step.</p></li></div>
	<div class="Rcolumn" style="height:5em;">
		<li><p>The appraiser completes the report and sends it to us.</p></li></div>
	<div class="Lcolumn">
		<li><p>You sign the loan papers, near your home or work, with one of our
		representatives.</p></li></div>
	<div class="Rcolumn">
		<li><p>Your loan is funded, and then we all SMILE!</p></li></div></ul>
	<br style="clear: both;">
	<hr>
